practices.description:
Dr. Michael Kirsch has been named NJ Top Dentist 2013; Best of Caldwell Dentist 2013 and honored to be a Healing Heroes Network Oral & Maxillofacial Surgery provider.

Michael H Kirsch, D.D.S., George W. Sandau, D.M.D., M.D., and Benjamin Jacobs, D.M.D.have many years of experience and expertise with all phases of dental implant rehabilitation, Teeth-In-A-Day dental implants, reconstructive bone grafting, wisdom tooth removal, dental extractions, and in-office general anesthesia and IV sedation. They diagnose and treat cysts and tumors of the jaws and mouth, facial pain, TMJ disorders and snoring.

The doctors are trained in laser surgery, CT scan dental implant diagnosis and treatment planning, virtual implant surgery, state-of-the-art digital imaging and electronic medical records. Their dedicated and experienced team are specially trained to help their patients will all facets of care including coordinating appointments with their dentists, maximizing insurance benefits, communicating with referring doctors, payment options and much more.
